|---|---|
| [d3-charts.js](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/frontend/static/js/d3-charts.js) | Add `drawBarChart()` function (~100 lines) |
| [charts.html](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/frontend/templates/charts.html) | Add a `<div id="publisherChart">` section |
| [app.js](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/frontend/static/js/app.js) | Add `loadPublisherBarChart()` in [initChartsPage()](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/frontend/static/js/app.js#594-605) |

### Testing
- Render publisher chart with data from `GET /api/charts/publishers/bar`
- Verify bars are grouped, y-axis starts from 0, tooltips show on hover
- Resize window — SVG must scale with `viewBox`

