2. Charts comparison page needs server-side search (Dev A will consume this)

### Acceptance Criteria
- [x] Fix [add_header()](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/backend/app.py#76-83) — remove the conflicting line. Keep `no-cache` for development, or use `max-age=300` for production
- [x] Verify conference/journal search routes accept queries from the comparison page (they already do — just needs testing)

### Code Fix
```diff
# app.py
     @app.after_request
     def add_header(r):
         r.headers["Cache-Control"] = "no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate"
         r.headers["Pragma"] = "no-cache"
         r.headers["Expires"] = "0"
-        r.headers['Cache-Control'] = 'public, max-age=0'
         return r
```

