| [06_match_journals.py](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/etl/06_match_journals.py) | Add conservative alias/override support if needed |
| [journal_manual_aliases.csv](file:///c:/Users/public.LAPTOP-17PSCTIQ/Desktop/MATHIMATA/proxorimena/project/data/matched/journal_manual_aliases.csv) | Curated manual match/unmatch overrides for safe journal curation |
